{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Morent | Privacy & Policy{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
{% include "navbar.html.twig" %}

  <div class="container">
    <div class="privacy-policy">
      <h3 class="text-center">Privacy & Policy</h3>
      <div class="content">
        <p class="desc">This Privacy Policy describes how Morent collects, uses, and shares your personal information when you use our car rental mobile application and related services.</p>
      <div class="item">
        <h5>Information We Collect</h5>
        <p>We collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Information You Provide Directly:</li>
            <ul>
              <li>Account Information: When you create an account, we <b>collect</b> your name, email address, phone number, date of birth, driver's license information (including number, expiration date, and issuing state/country), and payment information.</li>
              <li>Rental Information: When you rent a car, we collect information about your rental, including pickup and return locations, dates and times, car type, and any additional services you request.</li>
              <li>Communications: We collect information you provide when you contact us for support or other inquiries.</li>
            </ul>
          <li>Information We Collect Automatically:</li>
          <ul>
            <li>Device Information: We collect information about the device you use to access the App, including device type, operating system, unique device identifiers, and mobile network information. </li>
            <li>Location Information: With your permission, we collect your device's location to facilitate car pickup and return, provide directions, and offer location-based services.</li>
            <li>Usage Information: We collect information about your use of the App, including the features you use, the pages you visit, and the time you spend using the App.</li>
            <li>Cookies and Similar Technologies: We use cookies and similar technologies to collect information about your activity on the App and personalize your experience.</li>
          </ul>
          <li>Information from Third Parties:</li>
          <ul>
            <li>We may receive information about you from third-party partners, such as payment processors and identity verification services.</li>
          </ul>
        </ul>
      </div>
      

      <div class="item">
        <h5>How We Use Your Information</h5>
        <p>We use your information for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Providing and Managing the Services: To process your rentals, manage your account, provide customer support, and communicate with you about your rentals.</li>
          <li>Improving the Services: To analyze usage patterns, identify and fix bugs, and develop new features.</li>
          <li>Personalizing Your Experience: To tailor the App's content and offers to your preferences.</li>
          <li>Marketing and Promotions: With your consent, to send you promotional emails and notifications about our Services and offers from our partners.</li>
          <li>Legal Compliance: To comply with applicable laws and regulations.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      
      <div class="item">
        <h5>Sharing Your Information</h5>
        <p>We may share your information with the following third parties:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Service Providers: We share information with service providers who assist us with payment processing, identity verification, customer support, and other business operations.</li>
          <li>Rental Partners: We share information with the car rental companies that provide the vehicles you rent through the App.</li>
          <li>Legal Authorities: We may disclose your information to legal authorities if required by law or legal process.</li>
          <li>Business Transfers: If we are involved in a merger, acquisition, or sale of all or a portion of our assets, your information may be transferred as part of that transaction.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      
      <div class="item">
        <h5>Your Choices</h5>
        <ul>
          <li>Location Information: You can control the App's access to your device's location in your device's settings.</li>
          <li>Marketing Communications: You can opt out of receiving marketing communications from us by following the unsubscribe instructions in our emails or by contacting us.</li>
          <li>Cookies: You can manage cookies in your browser settings.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="item">
        <h5>Security</h5>
        <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="item">
        <h5>Children's Privacy</h5>
        <p>Our Services are not intended for children <b>under the age of 18</b>. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under this age.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="item">
        <h5>Changes to this Privacy Policy</h5>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated policy on the App or by other means.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="item">
        <h5>Contact Us</h5>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>


